Sympathy Flowers







Justin passed away on Tuesday, August 19, 2014.
Justin was a resident of Olney, Illinois.
VISITATION: 9:30 a.m. ~ 11:00 a.m. Friday, August 22, 2014 at the First Christian Church, 206 North Range St., Oblong, IL.
CELEBRATION OF JUSTIN'S LIFE SERVICE: 11:00 a.m. Friday, August 22, 2014 at the First Christian Church, 206 North Range St., Oblong, IL. Burial will follow in the Mound Cemetery, rural Jasper County.











