        Ferguson, Justin K.
    



Aug 22, 2014
















































































OBLONG -- Justin K. "Fergy" Ferguson, 32, Olney, formerly of Oblong, farmhand, died Tuesday (Aug. 19, 2014). 
Celebration of Life services: 11 a.m. Friday, First Christian Church, Oblong. Visitation: 9:30 a.m. until services in the church. Burial: Mound Cemetery, Willow Hill. Arrangements by: Pulliam Funeral Home, Oblong. Memorials: Educational Fund for Brooklyn Sue Ferguson, c/o First National Bank of Olney. Send condolences: www.oblongfuneralhome.com.
















































